{"tid":1304233,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[急] 我有少少建議關於 連儂牆！","createTime":"2019-07-10T14:19:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T14:23:02.000Z","uid":215794,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"581c3a7161454a95a9801ab0b1988206034fb03e","tid":1304233,"uid":215794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:19:31.000Z","msg":"我想求吓你哋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好寫咁多<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">惡毒仇恨</span></span>嘅說話<br />\n只會令 淺黃／淺藍 反感<br />\n<br />\n寫 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">激勵</span></span> 嘅說話可以形聚民氣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n令冷漠者也可以參與<br />\n從而影響佢哋嘅意向<br />\n<br />\n寫 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">事實</span></span> 可以辨明真相 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n令人知道另一方面的事實<br />\n從而懷疑反思身邊所接觸的媒體<br />\n<br />\n貼 <span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">娛樂性</span></span> 的事情可以增加話題性 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如 撕紙王／恥笑警犬<br />\n但係語調係<ins>偏向嘲諷</ins> 而唔係惡毒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係見到小部分 係純粹為發洩<br />\n係真係 大大隻字 一張Memo紙一隻字 寫<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「屌你老母」</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「死全家」</span><br />\n好似追數咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n𠵱啲喺公眾地方見到真係會反感 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你唔會屌到藍絲嘅人／警犬<br />\n因為佢哋基本上無眼睇<br />\n反而入目者係途人／同路人<br />\n亦都對事情無甚幫助<br />\n<br />\n大家可唔可以保持返少少6月大型活動時嘅克制<br />\n啫係 會同 同路人講Sorry<br />\n屌同路人亦唔會爆粗<br />\n<br />\n唔同意請屌我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同意請提醒連儂牆巴絲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e7688064c74f4504b3828abb0d62a21d4e30143","tid":1304233,"uid":215794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:20:37.000Z","msg":"我知大家想發洩<br />\n但可唔可以唔好寫咁大隻字 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96fd811ac91f89e4e896efd57a46a3848c59ef52","tid":1304233,"uid":260296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:21:04.000Z","msg":"長期快樂抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6059defa5c8927db7e9573266df3a9c055ffa908","tid":1304233,"uid":215794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96fd811ac91f89e4e896efd57a46a3848c59ef52","tid":1304233,"uid":260296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:21:04.000Z","msg":"長期快樂抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:23:02.000Z","msg":"本身都同意有啲巴打講<br />\n「唔好再著眼喺連儂牆打飛機」<br />\n<br />\n但𠵱個係俾之後仲要寫嘅人睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}